com.golden.gamedev.engine.graphics
Class NullGraphics

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Graphics
      java.awt.Graphics2D
          com.golden.gamedev.engine.graphics.NullGraphics
Direct Known Subclasses:
JOGLGraphics, LWJGLGraphics
public abstract class NullGraphics
extends Graphics2D

A fake Graphics2D class for OpenGL architecture.

The new graphics engine, in this case OpenGL architecture, should override all essential functions.
